///////////////////
functional
> Dumb component
> only use for display purpose
> Cannot maintain state

Class
> Logical Component
> Use for logics, display as well as api calling
> We can maintain state


Hooks

/////
State
> Act like a local varibale
> Any data interaction will happen through state
> Each component can have its own state
> We can update the value of state

Props
> Help to transfer data between component two nested component
> we cannot update the value of props

parent > child (props)
child > parent (props with function)

params
> what we pass after / 
> we need to declare in the route
> if declared complusolry to pass
> use for 1 or 2 values

queryparams
> what we pass after ?
> No Need to declare
> Not Complusory to pass
> Use for passing multiple values


history > redireaction
location > getting query params value
match > getting  params value

